🎮 Compita com outros em jogos multijogador baseados em atrações reais
🍺 Experimente o novo jogo Barrel Hunt para uma diversão no estilo pega-pega
💀 Una-se em combates cooperativos assustadores no Haunting Grounds
🐾 Adote animais de estimação fofinhos
🧍‍♂️ Personalize seu avatar e mostre seu estilo

🎮 Соревнуйтесь с другими в многопользовательских играх, основанных на реальных аттракционах

🐾 Заводите милых питомцев
🧍‍♂️ Кастомизируйте аватар и демонстрируйте свой стиль

🍺 Prueba el nuevo juego Barrel Hunt para una diversión al estilo “pilla-pilla”

🐾 Adopta adorables mascotas

👻 Get ready for the Spooktoberfest and try out our newest Spooky Castle ride and Crazy Maze! 🎃

🎮 Compete with others in multiplayer games based on real attractions

Grab your friends - there’s always something happening at Spooktoberfest!

Join the community: bit.ly/OktoberfestVRDiscord

🎢 Découvre des manèges fous & l’ambiance de la fête foraine

nodes.long_description:
The world's most famous and oldest folk festival - the Munich Oktoberfest - is all about fun and socializing. Munich Oktoberfest - The Official Game brings these aspects into virtual reality as the worlds first social VR fun fair. Here it is possible to explore a virtual version of the festival together with friends and players from all over the world.

Join the virtual Oktoberfest to interact with other players, play hilarious multiplayer games and experience the true atmosphere of the Oktoberfest. Have fun working as a beer hall employee to earn your place in the hall of fame as quickest bartender or experience the spectacular motion rides together with your friends.

Of course authentic dressing in Bavarian costumes for your virtual Oktoberfest visit is also possible! So get your Lederhosen or Drindl ready and join the fun today!
